          "range": "2872-2971",
          "rangeStart": 2872,
          "rangeEnd": 2971,
          "markText": "在加速的社会中，每个人都在为了将来努力，但将来是什么样并不确定。唯一确定的是“过去拥有的”。于是乎，透支——努力将想象的未来提前到当下实现，赶紧将当下变成为确定的过去——成了人们社会生活的基本逻辑。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1749873877,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-14 12:04:37",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2872&rangeEnd=2971",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2872&rangeEnd=2971"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_1658-1736",
          "range": "1658-1736",
          "rangeStart": 1658,
          "rangeEnd": 1736,
