    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_4_1707-1751",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1707-1751",
      "markText": "专业”本身就意味着一种知识权力；越是强调专业化，也就意味着它所带来的信息不对称会越明显。",
      "totalCount": 774,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1707&rangeEnd=1751",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1707&rangeEnd=1751"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_2872-2971",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2872-2971",
      "markText": "在加速的社会中，每个人都在为了将来努力，但将来是什么样并不确定。唯一确定的是“过去拥有的”。于是乎，透支——努力将想象的未来提前到当下实现，赶紧将当下变成为确定的过去——成了人们社会生活的基本逻辑。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2872&rangeEnd=2971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2872&rangeEnd=2971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_4333-4415",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4333-4415",
      "markText": "近些年来，基层治理的一大特点是，各种治理事务都以攻坚、行动的方式限时完成，运动式治理泛化到了各种治理事务中。限时的目标、集中的力量、细小的事务之间，形成了诸多悖论。",
      "totalCount": 688,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4333&rangeEnd=4415",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4333&rangeEnd=4415"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_6_832-904",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "832-904",
      "markText": "所谓“会哭的孩子有奶吃”，又谓“大闹大解决，小闹小解决，不闹不解决”。人们普遍认为，出了点事不闹腾一番不正常。“闹”是常规，不闹反倒是不正常的。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=832&rangeEnd=904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=832&rangeEnd=904"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_7_5450-5512",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5450-5512",
      "markText": "而政府更需要做的，是鼓励和支持相关企业开发经济实用的清洁能源及设备，并做好基础设施工作，让群众自己去选择更好的能源消费方式。",
      "totalCount": 658,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5450&rangeEnd=5512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5450&rangeEnd=5512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_3023-3100",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3023-3100",
      "markText": "今日，哪怕是最普通的农村青年，也要超前消费，提前实现“城市梦”：为了在城市买房、买车以及高消费，不仅要花光父辈的积蓄，还要透支父辈和自己未来的劳动力价值。",
      "totalCount": 608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3023&rangeEnd=3100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3023&rangeEnd=3100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_5_4668-4765",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4668-4765",
      "markText": "事实上，根据我们实地的调研发现，警察权益所受到的侵害（不公平感、待遇等），一点也不比别的群体差。所幸的是，公安机关是一个纪律部门，其政治性和组织性都比较强，不至于为了个人利益和群体利益而罔顾大局",
      "totalCount": 608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4668&rangeEnd=4765",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4668&rangeEnd=4765"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_4_2143-2176",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2143-2176",
      "markText": "从社会学视角看，反社会本身是文明的公敌，却又恰恰是文明进程的产物。",
      "totalCount": 546,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2143&rangeEnd=2176",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2143&rangeEnd=2176"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_6_3129-3218",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3129-3218",
      "markText": "首先还是要从基层政府自身做起。长期以来，“老好人”现象和“不出事逻辑”主导了基层治理。基层政府在“讨价还价”的过程中，往往无原则，以息事宁人为导向，最终培育了一大批特殊利益人群。",
      "totalCount": 546,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3129&rangeEnd=3218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3129&rangeEnd=3218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_668-702",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "668-702",
      "markText": "乡土社会的核心特征是稳定而静止，人与人之间、人与空间之间的关系稳定。",
      "totalCount": 512,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=702",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=702"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_3728-3753",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3728-3753",
      "markText": "基层社会的反应和诉求，也可以便捷地上达国家权力中心",
      "totalCount": 506,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3728&rangeEnd=3753",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3728&rangeEnd=3753"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_6_2829-2921",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2829-2921",
      "markText": "但是，对社会主要矛盾的处理方法仍停留在旧有思维中：习惯于用“大局观”来说服群众作出“牺牲”；习惯于一时一策、一事一议，用权宜之计来解决社会矛盾。结果是，解决的问题越多，留下的隐患越大。",
      "totalCount": 500,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2829&rangeEnd=2921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2829&rangeEnd=2921"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_4243-4304",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4243-4304",
      "markText": "许多地方政府也在以透支的逻辑展开治理活动，通过金融杠杆，以政府信用和土地资源为依托，为了眼前的“政绩”而不惜付出长远代价。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4304",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4243&rangeEnd=4304"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_4_3635-3699",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3635-3699",
      "markText": "社会安全的重心不在于国家依靠暴力机关尤其是一整套惩戒机构去清除可能的反社会因素，而是要着力于修复社会，让社会有能力自己解决风险。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3635&rangeEnd=3699",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3635&rangeEnd=3699"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_2512-2595",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2512-2595",
      "markText": "在一个时间概念模糊、日常生活周而复始的乡土社会中，人际关系稳定而有预期，互惠原则主导了社会关系。然而，一旦时间被精准切割且赋予价值，则社会生活本身也成了被算计的对象。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039330&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2512&rangeEnd=2595",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/57e32aa0813ab75ddg010a4d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2512&rangeEnd=2595"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039330_3_4464-4540",
